-- Mexico Arrests Eight in Connection With August's Killing of 72 Immigrants
-- B y   A n d r e s   R .   M a r t i n e z
-- 2010-10-16T19:40:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-16/mexico-arrests-eight-in-connection-with-august-s-killing-of-72-immigrants.html
Mexico’s attorney general’s office
said eight people have been arrested in connection with the case
of 72 immigrants who were found dead in the northern part of the
nation in August.  The eight people were arrested in separate operations, the
attorney general’s office said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andres R. Martinez at 
 amartinez28@bloomberg.net  